review_blob: Huge tropical nose that goes on and on. Creamy mouthfeel that sticks to your tongue. Hoppy bitterness up front, then rounds out at the end. Beautiful balance between Carmel malts and hoppy resin. A great summer...no, anytime beer!

Poured into a tulip glass. Color is cloudy gold, bright and beautiful. Explosion of pine, sweet freshness on the nose. Mouthfeel is pleasant. Hoppy, fresh, balanced and delicious! I'll have another one!
